    "content": "This tab is not perfect but it gets the job done.\r\nThe key notes in the main riff are the F# on the 2 and then the 2-4-5.\r\nInstead of sliding back from 9 you can always just play F# on the 1 just like in the \r\nmeasure of the song.\r\nPlay around with the second part of the main riff to see if there's something you like better.\r\n\r\n[tab]Intro:  (Main riff)\r\nG|----------------|----------------|-----------------|----------------|\r\nD|----------------|----------------|-----------------|----------------|\r\nA|----------------|----------7-----|9\\---------------|----------7-----|\r\nE|2---2-------2-4-|5-------7---7-0-|----2--------2-4-|5-------7---7-0-|[/tab]\r\n\r\n[tab]G|-----------------|----------------|-----------------|----------------|\r\nD|-----------------|----------------|-----------------|----------------|\r\nA|9\\---------------|----------7-----|9\\---------------|----------7-----|\r\nE|-----2-------2-4-|5-------7---7-0-|----2--------2-4-|5-------7---7-0-|[/tab]\r\n\r\n[tab]Verse 1:\r\nG|----------------|----------------|----------------|----------------|\r\nD|4-4-4---4-4-4---|--------------2-|4-4-4---4-4-4---|--------------2-|\r\nA|------4---------|0-----2-4-2-----|------4---------|0-----2-4-2-----|\r\nE|--------------4-|----------------|--------------4-|----------------|\r\nx2[/tab]\r\n\r\n[tab]Pre-Chorus:  (slides vary, I always play them on 2)\r\n\"Honey, it don't really matter to me\u2026\"\r\nG|----------------|----------------|----------------|-------------------|\r\nD|----------------|----------------|----------------|-------------------|\r\nA|5~--------------|---/12----------|2~--------------|---/14----14-14-14-|\r\nE|----------------|----------------|----------------|-------------------|[/tab]\r\n\r\n[tab]Chorus:\r\nG|----------------|----------------|----------------|----------------|\r\nD|----------------|----------------|----------------|----------------|\r\nA|----------------|----------7-----|9\\--------------|----------7-----|\r\nE|2---2-------2-4-|5-------7---7-0-|---2--------2-4-|5-------7---7-0-|[/tab]\r\n\r\nVerse 2: Repeat Verse 1\r\n\r\nPre-Chorus 2: Repeat Pre-Chorus 1\r\n\r\nChorus 2:  Repeat Chorus 1 x2\r\n\r\n[tab]Bridge:\r\nG|----------------|-----------------|----------------|9/11\\9-9-7---6---|\r\nD|----------------|9/11\\9-9-7---6---|----------------|---------------7-|\r\nA|----------------|---------------7-|0---0---0---0---|-----------------|\r\nE|0---0---0---0---|-----------------|----------------|-----------------|[/tab]\r\n\r\n[tab]G|----------------|----------------|----------------|------------------------|\r\nD|0---0---0---0---|7/9\\7-7-5---4---|---------------/|14-14-14----14----14----|\r\nA|----------------|--------------5-|-------/7-7-7---|---------14----14----14-|\r\nE|----------------|----------------|0-0-0-----------|------------------------|[/tab]\r\n\r\n[tab]G|----------------|----------------|-----------------|----------------|\r\nD|----------------|----------------|-----------------|----------------|\r\nA|----------------|----------7-----|9\\---------------|----------7-----|\r\nE|2---2-------2-4-|5-------7---7-0-|----2--------2-4-|5-------7---7-0-|[/tab]\r\n\r\n[tab]G|----------------|----------------|-----------------|----------------|\r\nD|----------------|----------------|-----------------|----------------|\r\nA|9\\--------------|----------7-----|9\\---------------|----------7-----|\r\nE|----2-------2-4-|5-------7---7-0-|----2--------2-4-|5-------7---7-0-|[/tab]\r\n\r\nVerse 3: Same as Verse 1 and Verse 2\r\n\r\nPre-Chorus 3: Same as Pre-Chorus 1 and 2\r\n\r\n[tab]Chorus 3: similar to 1 and 2, main riff continues on until song ends.\r\nG|----------------|----------------|-----------------|----------------|\r\nD|----------------|----------------|-----------------|----------------|\r\nA|----------------|----------7-----|9\\---------------|----------7-----|\r\nE|2---2-------2-4-|5-------7---7-0-|----2--------2-4-|5-------7---7-0-|[/tab]\r\n\r\n[tab]G|-----------------|----------------|-----------------|----------------|\r\nD|-----------------|----------------|-----------------|----------------|\r\nA|9\\---------------|----------7-----|9\\---------------|----------7-----|\r\nE|-----2-------2-4-|5-------7---7-0-|----2--------2-4-|5-------7---7-0-|[/tab]\r\n\r\n[tab]G|----------------|----------------|-----------------|----------------|\r\nD|----------------|----------------|-----------------|----------------|\r\nA|----------------|----------7-----|9\\---------------|----------7-----|\r\nE|2---2-------2-4-|5-------7---7-0-|----2--------2-4-|5-------7---7-0-|[/tab]\r\n\r\nOutro:  Continue playing main riff until song fades out.",
